mp3-archive NEWS

===========================================================================
v20260329 (2026-03-29)
===========================================================================

New features
------------
- Genre, year, comment fields added to DB and extracted from audio tags
- Search now covers genre, year, comment in addition to existing fields
- "태그 포함" checkbox: toggle between filename-only and full-tag search
  (default: filename-only)
- File path shown as a dedicated "경로" column in the main table
- Column visibility toggle: right-click any table header to show/hide columns;
  state is persisted across sessions via QSettings
- Tooltips added to all buttons, controls, and table cells

Bug fixes
---------
- song_info_dialog and tag_detail_dialog added to PyInstaller hiddenimports

===========================================================================
v20260328 (2026-03-28) — third batch
===========================================================================

New features
------------
- Support for FLAC, OGG, WAV, M4A, WMA, Opus in addition to MP3
- MusicBrainz tag lookup: "태그 찾기" button auto-fills missing tags
- Right-click context menu on table rows:
    - "자세히": show all embedded tags from the file
    - "인터넷에서 정보 보기": MusicBrainz song info popup
    - "태그 찾기": fetch and apply tags for that row
- Duration displayed in m:ss format (e.g. 1:40 instead of 100s)
- Column sorting by clicking table headers
- PyInstaller spec files for Windows and Linux standalone builds

Bug fixes
---------
- Fixed ModuleNotFoundError for urllib in PyInstaller build
- Fixed spec file path resolution using SPECPATH

===========================================================================
v20260328 (2026-03-28) — second batch
===========================================================================

New features
------------
- Real-time search as user types (textChanged signal)
- Keyword search across filename, title, artist, album
- More natural Korean button labels (빠른 스캔 / 전체 스캔 / 삭제)

===========================================================================
v20260328 (2026-03-28) — initial release
===========================================================================

Initial release.

Features
--------
- Recursive MP3 scan with SQLite metadata storage
- Incremental scan (skip unchanged files) and force full rescan
- Filename fallback parser: "Artist - Title.mp3" when ID3 tags are absent
- File creation/modification timestamp tracking
- Persistent scan path via QSettings
- Record deletion
- PyQt6 desktop UI with Qt Designer layout
